<h1>Welcome to Shelfworm, <%= user.gr_full_name %>!</h1>

<div class="welcome">
  <p>Please take a moment to select a username on Shelfworm that will serve as your custom URL on our site.</p>
  <p>For example, if you pick the name "mister_bigglesworth", your public Shelfworm bookshelf will be accessible at www.shelfworm.com/mister_bigglesworth .  </p>
  <p>The name must begin with a letter and can't contain any special characters.</p>
  <p>Note you can only make this selection once! </p>

  <form action='/profile/<%= user.gr_id %>/register' method='post'>
    <input type='text' name='username' placeholder='Username...' pattern="^[a-zA-Z][a-zA-Z0-9-_\.]{1,20}$" autofocus required/>
    <input class="button button-3d" type='submit' value='Create Account'/>
  </form>

</div>